<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>컴퓨터 활용 및 코딩 학습</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap-icons/1.5.0/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1 class="text-center">컴퓨터 활용 및 코딩 학습 콘텐츠</h1>
        
        <!-- 컴퓨터활용 카테고리 -->
        <h2 class="mt-5">컴퓨터 활용</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="https://code.org/images/pre-reader-express-course-banner.png" class="card-img-top" alt="마우스 클릭연습(기초)">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">마우스 클릭연습(기초)</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">마우스 클릭연습</p>
                        <a href="https://studio.code.org/s/pre-express-2022/lessons/1/levels/1" class="btn btn-primary">시작하기</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="https://blockly.games/index/puzzle.png" class="card-img-top" alt="마우스 클릭연습(블럭)">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">마우스 클릭연습(블럭)</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">블럭에 속성을 입력하여 알맞게 코딩해보세요</p>
                        <a href="https://blockly.games/puzzle?lang=ko" class="btn btn-primary">시작하기</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 마인크래프트 카테고리 -->
        <h2 class="mt-5">마인크래프트</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="https://code.org/images/mc/minecraft-activity-aquatic.png" class="card-img-top" alt="수중세계 탐험">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">수중세계 탐험</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">수중 세계를 탐험하며 문제 해결 능력을 발휘해보세요.</p>
                        <a href="https://studio.code.org/s/aquatic/lessons/1/levels/1" class="btn btn-primary">시작하기</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="https://code.org/images/mc/minecraft-activity-journey.png" class="card-img-top" alt="히어로의 여정">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">히어로의 여정</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">에이전트에게 명령을 내리고 장애물을 극복하세요.</p>
                        <a href="https://studio.code.org/s/hero/lessons/1/levels/1" class="btn btn-primary">시작하기</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="https://code.org/images/mc/minecraft-activity-adventurer.png" class="card-img-top" alt="어드벤처러">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">어드벤처러</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">코드를 작성해 마인크래프트 세계를 탐험하세요.</p>
                        <a href="https://studio.code.org/s/mc/lessons/1/levels/1" class="btn btn-primary">시작하기</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 블록리게임 카테고리 -->
        <h2 class="mt-5">블록리게임</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="https://blockly.games/index/maze.png" class="card-img-top" alt="미로">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">미로</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">while 조건문을 활용해 자동길찾기 로직을 완성해보세요.</p>
                        <a href="https://blockly.games/maze?lang=ko" class="btn btn-primary">시작하기</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="https://blockly.games/index/bird.png" class="card-img-top" alt="새">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">새</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">각도와 조건문을 활용해 새가 먹이를 찾아 둥지까지 가도록 코딩해보세요.</p>
                        <a href="https://blockly.games/bird?lang=ko" class="btn btn-primary">시작하기</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="https://blockly.games/index/turtle.png" class="card-img-top" alt="거북이">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">거북이</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">각도와 반복문을 활용해 도형그리기를 완성해보세요.</p>
                        <a href="https://blockly.games/turtle?lang=ko" class="btn btn-primary">시작하기</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/public/header.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
